# modify for fizzbuzz++

openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: FizzBuzz++
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
  # TODO
  - url: http://petstore.swagger.io/v1
paths:
  /game:
    get:
      summary: List of String integers or Fizz/Buzz/Bazz
      operationId: listFizz
      tags:
        - fizz
      parameters:
        - name: limit
          in: query
          description: How many items to return at one time (max 100)
          required: false
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
      responses:
        '200':
          description: List of String integers or Fizz/Buzz/Bazz
          content:
            application/json:    
              schema:
                $ref: "#/Game"
        # TODO
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Error"
Game:
  required:
    - n
  properties:
    n:
      type: integer
      format: int64
